data.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom home close to the community park! This one-story property welcomes you w/gorgeous curb appeal, low maintenance  front yard w/desert landscaping. Come inside to see vaulted ceilings making entertaining a breeze, durable tile floors, plus an ample family room &  backyard access, merging indoor/outdoor activities. The updated immaculate kitchen showcases SS appliances, white cabinetry, a combination of pendant & track lighting, an oversized  breakfast bar, and an intimate dining area. Discover a main retreat w/spacious walk-in closet & an ensuite boasting new marble counter w/new hardware & dual undermount sinks. Secondary bedrooms roomy & updated hall bath. Private serene & easy maintenance large backyard w/covered patio, a lovely paver seating area, &  artificial turf. Great location near to I-10 freeway access, close to the BLVD, shopping, restaurants & schools
